d our affiliates have focused on meeting our patients’ healthcare needs in all of the communities we serve the company operates through its subsidiaries more than  acute care hospitals behavioral health facilities and ambulatory centers in the us puerto rico the us virgin islands and the united kingdom our more than  dedicated and talented employees treat more than  million people each year with dignity and respect we recognize that the patients we serve come to us at the most vulnerable times in their lives and we put them first every day and help them achieve their best possible outcome our consistent growth correlates directly to our focus on providing the highest level of patient care resulting in more patients and referring physicians choosing us patients are our first priority we take pride in our strong patient satisfaction scores that continually increase we have high standards for quality in   uhs acute care and behavioral health facilities rated as top performers on key quality measures® for  the last time this recognition was awarded by the joint commission an independent notforprofit organization that accredits and certifies healthcare organizations and programs uhs has a deep commitment to the communities we serve and we actively raise awareness of critical healthcare issues fortune magazine consistently lists uhs among its “worlds most admired companies” among our peer group we have ranked  with regard to social responsibility as well as in longterm investment most recently forbes ranked uhs  in its inaugural list of america’s top  companies we continuously invest so that we can continue to provide care over the past three years we have invested more than  billion in our facilities explore more board of directors corporate information corporate officers corporate strategy mission statement timeline uhs th anniversary uhs annual report archive uhs awards and recognition uhs supply chain giving our patients top priority hear what patients say search jobs