he uhs name it has been brought to our attention that a handful of cases have occurred around the country where scammers using the uhs name have attempted to lure unsuspecting job seekers into an arrangement whereby they would be asked to send money in exchange for a job with the company this is a scam targeting job seekers and the individuals involved are not representatives of uhs if you are the victim of such a scam we ask that you notify the uhs compliance department at  notify local law enforcement authorities the recruiting website and google being certain to include the email address of those who you were corresponding with if you receive any checks do not cash them instead contact the bank and inform them that you believe that you have received a fraudulent check and want to report it lead inspire succeed if you want to work for a company where you can build the career of your dreams uhs may be the place for you if you are looking for a place where you can build the career of your dreams uhs may be the place for you at uhs were looking for exceptional people who share our vision and values who share our focus on hard work enthusiasm teamwork loyalty trust and cooperation weve embraced these traits and built a team of employees who consistently work to achieve the highest level of service excellence people are our most valuable resource at uhs as we are committed to providing high quality acute care and behavioral health services to residents of the communities we serve we are equally committed to offering our employees unlimited opportunity in an environment that encourages professional development opportunity to grow we know that providing a professional working environment and an opportunity to grow is a key to attracting and retaining talented motivated employees thats why we provide encouragement and support to employees who want to expand their knowledge and increase their proficiency through continuing education and jobrelated training  service excellence drives uhs every uhs employee takes part in our service excellence program and are guided by three standards treat everyone as a guest demonstrate professionalism and excellence in the things i do practice teamwork these standards help ensure that the staff at all uhs acute care hospitals and behavioral health facilities deliver high quality care to every patient education and career planning the behavioral health division of uhs recently added the psychiatry residency  fellowship education and career planning program this unique complimentary program offers exclusive educational opportunities to residents and fellows by assisting them in navigating where business and medicine intertwine learn more about the program pdf  search opportunities online  explore more search jobs benefits commitment to service excellence executive successes equal opportunity employer arc  alternative resolution of conflicts outlook web app to use outlook web app browser settings must allow scripts to run for information about how to allow scripts consult the help for your browser if your browser doesnt support scripts you can download windows internet explorer for access to outlook web app universal health services inc  nyseuhs  stock quote  news  thestreet action alerts plus access aapjim cramers best stocks for charitable trust portfoliomost recent trade alert investing rules trading commandments real money access rm rules of investingjim cramers best stocks for  commandmentsstressed out stockscramers blog cramer mad money etfs futures markets much more banksbiotechretailtechpersonal financeretirementfinancial advisor centerhow to spendoptionsfixed incomevideo privacy policyterms of use  thestreet inc all rights reserved djia nasdaq sp  market data updated sign in your memberships your account account preferences alerts newsletters subscribe logout subscribe access insights and guidance from our wall street pros find the product thats right for you action alerts plus action alerts o